(1.  **Frontend Layer:** A single-page application built using **Vite, React, Tailwind CSS**, and **Shadcn UI**. Uses) Tj
T* (**Recharts** for visualizing delivery timelines, risk vectors, and multi-agent interaction sequences. Communicates) Tj
T* (with the API Gateway via secure WebSockets and HTTPS.) Tj
ET
BT
/F1 9.5 Tf
10.9249999999999989 TL
0.2 0.255 0.333 rg
56.6929133858267775 411.8987433070865336 Td
(2.  **Backend API Gateway \(Node.js + Express\):** Handles client-facing requests, serves as the gatekeeper for) Tj
T* (user authentication, coordinates session management, and schedules high-throughput data sync jobs.) Tj
ET
BT
/F1 9.5 Tf
10.9249999999999989 TL
0.2 0.255 0.333 rg
56.6929133858267775 369.2392535433070293 Td
(3.  **FastAPI Multi-Agent Engine:** A dedicated Python microservice designed to host the multi-agent LLM) Tj
T* (coordination frameworks \(e.g., using **LangGraph** or **CrewAI** structures\). It connects with Redis for distributed) Tj
T* (task queuing and runs the dynamic contextual memory systems.) Tj
ET
BT
/F1 9.5 Tf
10.9249999999999989 TL
0.2 0.255 0.333 rg
56.6929133858267775 313.7539559055117024 Td
(4.  **Database Layer \(PostgreSQL with `pgvector`\):** Contains the primary operational relational schema along) Tj
T* (with vector representations of ingested communication fragments, tasks, and commits to support rapid, low-latency) Tj
T* (semantic semantic searches.) Tj
ET
BT
/F1 9.5 Tf
10.9249999999999989 TL
0.2 0.255 0.333 rg
56.6929133858267775 258.2686582677164324 Td
(5.  **Data Isolation & Compliance Boundary \(PII Masking Gateway\):** Built directly into the ingestion and outbound) Tj
T* (egress pipeline. Relies on deterministic string verification alongside a local SpaCy NER model to scrubbing) Tj
T* (sensitive customer records prior to transferring metrics to the foundational model services.) Tj
ET
